(3, 'admin_solar_ecom', '2023-01-01', 'Min Lwin Kyaw', 'Admin Dashboard (Solar Ecom)', '', '', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/minlwinkyaw/image/upload/v1593643415/minlwinkyaw/Job_posting_site/thumbnail_wwhjnr.jpg', '<div class=\\\"btom-cont1 pt-4\\\">\\r\\n                            <h2 class=\\\"py-3\\\">Project\'s Info<\\/h2>\\r\\n                            <p class=\\\"p-l-3\\\">\\r\\n                            <ul class=\\\"px-4\\\">\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Name<\\/span> : Job Posting Website\\r\\n                                <\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Team Members<\\/span> : Min Lwin Kyaw<\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Duration<\\/span> : 1 Month<\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Programming Languages & Frameworks<\\/span> : Django, Python, HTML, CSS, JavaScript\\r\\n                                <\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Platforms<\\/span> : Web\\r\\n                                <\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Links<\\/span> :\\r\\n                                    <a target=\\\"_blank\\\"\\r\\n                                       href=\\\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/Minlwinkyaw307\\/job_posting_site\\/\\\">GitHub(Source Code)<\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/li>\\r\\n                            <\\/ul>\\r\\n                            <\\/p>\\r\\n                            <p class=\\\"text-justify py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                It is a web application for posting jobs and allow people who are looking for job to apply.\\r\\n                                Included CMS for client and developer in project. Project was done by using Django, python,\\r\\n                          