                                   alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                                    <\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <h6><b>Jobs<\\/b><\\/h6>\\r\\n                                    <p class=\\\"text-justify\\\">\\r\\n                                        In jobs page, at the top of the page there is search and filter option to search job or filter jobs base of region or type of job which user is looking for. That\'s part is done by AJAX.\\r\\n                                    <\\/p>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593293139\\/minlwinkyaw\\/Job_posting_site\\/4_ckm6rq.png\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-lightbox=\\\"job_posting_site\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-title=\\\"Jobs List\\\">\\r\\n                                        <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593293139\\/minlwinkyaw\\/Job_posting_site\\/4_ckm6rq.png\\\"\\r\\n                                             class=\\\"img-responsive img-fluid\\\"\\r\\n                                             alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                                    <\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <h6><b>Jobs (Job List)<\\/b><\\/h6>\\r\\n                                    <p class=\\\"text-justify\\\">\\r\\n                                        In this section of the jobs page, it list the jobs the same way as home page job list but it include category filter option which is also work with top filter option to filter out job base on category.\\r\\n                                    <\\/p>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593300979\\/minlwinkyaw\\/Job_posting_site\\/11_prcuxp.png\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-lightbox=\\\"job_posting_site\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-title=\\\"Job Detail\\\">\\r\\n                                        <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593300979\\/minlwinkyaw\\/Job_posting_site\\/11_prcuxp.png\\\"\\r\\n                                             class=\\\"img-responsive img-fluid\\\"\\r\\n                                             alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                                    <\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <h6><b>Job Detail<\\/b><\\/h6>\\r\\n                                    <p class=\\\"text-justify\\\">\\r\\n                                        In the job detail page, it show detail of the jobs using slider of image, and other information like salary, city, type of job, requirement, gender for the role, deadline, what kind of things going to need and do in the job.\\r\\n                                    <\\/p>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593293190\\/minlwinkyaw\\/Job_posting_site\\/5_klmey2.png\\\"\\r\\n                                  