jobs, comment and saved jobs.\\r\\n                                    <\\/p>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593293390\\/minlwinkyaw\\/Job_posting_site\\/9_ufoyrs.png\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-lightbox=\\\"job_posting_site\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-title=\\\"Admin-1\\\">\\r\\n                                        <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593293390\\/minlwinkyaw\\/Job_posting_site\\/9_ufoyrs.png\\\"\\r\\n                                             class=\\\"img-responsive img-fluid\\\"\\r\\n                                             alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                                    <\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593293349\\/minlwinkyaw\\/Job_posting_site\\/8_pfbnym.png\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-lightbox=\\\"job_posting_site\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-title=\\\"Admin-2\\\">\\r\\n                                        <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593293349\\/minlwinkyaw\\/Job_posting_site\\/8_pfbnym.png\\\"\\r\\n                                             class=\\\"img-responsive img-fluid\\\"\\r\\n                                             alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                                    <\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <h6><b>Admin<\\/b><\\/h6>\\r\\n                                    <p class=\\\"text-justify\\\">\\r\\n                                        I am using Django Admin to control, adding, editing, updating and deleting data for the project. I am using it for the development purpose only.\\r\\n                                    <\\/p>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n                            <\\/div>\\r\\n                        <\\/div>', 15),
(4, 'steganography_for_images', '2020-05-01', 'Min Lwin Kyaw', 'Steganography For Images', 'Steganography For Images', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/minlwinkyaw/image/upload/v1593401776/minlwinkyaw/steganography/banner_xd4rky.png', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/minlwinkyaw/image/upload/v1593644524/minlwinkyaw/steganography/thumbnail_prnora.jpg', '<div class=\\\"btom-cont1 pt-4\\\">\\r\\n                            <h2 class=\\\"py-3\\\">Project\'s Info<\\/h2>\\r\\n                            <p class=\\\"p-l-3\\\">\\r\\n                            <ul class=\\\"px-4\\\">\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Name<\\/span> : Steganography For Images\\r\\n\\r\\n                                <\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Team Members<\\/span> : Min Lwin Kyaw<\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Duration<\\/span> : 2 Days<\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Programming Languages & Frameworks<\\/span> : Python\\r\\n                                <\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Platforms<\\/span> : Cross-Platform\\r\\n                                <\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Links<\\/span> :\\r\\n                                    <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/Minlwinkyaw307\\/steganography_with_image\\\">GitHub<\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/li>\\r\\n                            <\\/ul>\\r\\n                            <\\/p>\\r\\n                            <p class=\\\"text-justify py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                A cross-platform application to hide one small image to another big image to by using bit level\\r\\n                                data encryption or password base encryption on bit level encrypted image. Project was done by\\r\\n                                using python, and image processing.\\r\\n                            <\\/p>\\r\\n                            <div class=\\\"row\\\">\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593401104\\/minlwinkyaw\\/steganography\\/2_le44es.png\\\" data-lightbox=\\\"steganography\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-title=\\\"Main Page\\\">\\r\\n                                        <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593401104\\/minlwinkyaw\\/steganography\\/2_le44es.png\\\" class=\\\"img-responsive img-fluid\\\"\\r\\n                                             alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                                    <\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <h6><b>Main Page<\\/b><\\/h6>\\r\\n                                    <p class=\\\"text-justify\\\">\\r\\n                                        In the application, user can insert one image as base image(bigger image that big enough to hide small one) and secret image(small image that small enough to hide inside base image).\\r\\n                                        User can use reversed XOR(encryption method that I created) or plain to hide image.\\r\\n                                        <br> Support three different output image types - png, tiff, bmp (jpg will compress the image before saving it, so, it will break stored bit values and result will be different. That\'s why I used these formats for save image).\\r\\n                                        <br>\\r\\n                                        To reversed secret image from steganography image, if image used reversed XOR encryption, then need to select reversed XOR encryption, if not just select none and decrypt image from it.\\r\\n\\r\\n                                    <\\/p>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n                            <\\/div>\\r\\n                        <\\/div>', 70);
