(5, 'online_food_order', '2019-12-01', 'Min Lwin Kyaw', 'Online Food Order For Restaurant', 'Online Food Order For Restaurant', '', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/minlwinkyaw/image/upload/v1593642968/minlwinkyaw/restaurant/thumbnail_tyry3j.jpg', '<div class=\\\"btom-cont1 pt-4\\\">\\r\\n                            <h2 class=\\\"py-3\\\">Project\'s Info<\\/h2>\\r\\n                            <p class=\\\"p-l-3\\\">\\r\\n                            <ul class=\\\"px-4\\\">\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Name<\\/span> : Online Food Order For Restaurant\\r\\n                                <\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Team Members<\\/span> : Min Lwin Kyaw<\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Duration<\\/span> : 3 Months<\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Programming Languages & Frameworks<\\/span> :\\r\\n                                    Symfony, PHP, HTML, JavaScript, MySQL\\r\\n                                <\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Platforms<\\/span> : Web\\r\\n                                <\\/li>\\r\\n                                <li><span class=\\\"project-detail-span\\\">Links<\\/span> :\\r\\n                                    <a target=\\\"_blank\\\"\\r\\n                                       href=\\\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/Minlwinkyaw307\\/st_1_project\\\">GitHub(Source Code)<\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/li>\\r\\n                            <\\/ul>\\r\\n                            <\\/p>\\r\\n                            <p class=\\\"text-justify py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                It is a web application restaurant owner to publish their foods, drinks, desserts, and\\r\\n                                others food\\r\\n                                related things on their website and allow user to order these foods and drink by using\\r\\n                                this\\r\\n                                website. Included CMS for customers and restaurant\\u2019s owners. Project was done by using\\r\\n                                Symfony, php, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript for Computer Special Topic 1 Course.<br>\\r\\n\\r\\n                                Because of course project, there are some limitation to follow to get perfect point.\\r\\n                                <br>\\r\\n                                Templates are downloaded from <a target=\\\"_blank\\\"\\r\\n                                                                 href=\\\"https:\\/\\/colorlib.com\\/\\\">Colorlib<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n                            <\\/p>\\r\\n                            <div class=\\\"row\\\">\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593403346\\/minlwinkyaw\\/restaurant\\/1_thhnbp.png\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-lightbox=\\\"online_food_order\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-title=\\\"Home Page - 1\\\">\\r\\n                                        <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593403346\\/minlwinkyaw\\/restaurant\\/1_thhnbp.png\\\"\\r\\n                                             class=\\\"img-responsive img-fluid\\\"\\r\\n                                             alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                                    <\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <h6><b>Home Page - 1<\\/b><\\/h6>\\r\\n                                    <p class=\\\"text-justify\\\">\\r\\n                                        Because of course limitation, in home page it must have slider which is created\\r\\n                                        from the admin dashboard as admin wished, few recently added food list and some\\r\\n                                        content for website as most of the website usually does.\\r\\n                                        <br>\\r\\n                                        In menu, there are home, about us, preference, contact us, order meals (to find\\r\\n                                        all of the foods available in restaurant, sign in and sign up pages.\\r\\n                                    <\\/p>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593403346\\/minlwinkyaw\\/restaurant\\/2_osdzc0.png\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-lightbox=\\\"online_food_order\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-title=\\\"Home Page - 2\\\">\\r\\n                                        <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593403346\\/minlwinkyaw\\/restaurant\\/2_osdzc0.png\\\"\\r\\n                                             class=\\\"img-responsive img-fluid\\\"\\r\\n                                             alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                                    <\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <h6><b>Home Page - 2<\\/b><\\/h6>\\r\\n                                    <p class=\\\"text-justify\\\">\\r\\n                                        In this part of the home page, it list few foods with filter and sort option to\\r\\n                                        find latest food available in restaurant.\\r\\n                                    <\\/p>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593403345\\/minlwinkyaw\\/restaurant\\/3_b3evaw.png\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-lightbox=\\\"online_food_order\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-title=\\\"Meal Detail Page\\\">\\r\\n                                        <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593403345\\/minlwinkyaw\\/restaurant\\/3_b3evaw.png\\\"\\r\\n                                             class=\\\"img-responsive img-fluid\\\"\\r\\n                                             alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                                    <\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <h6><b>Meal Detail Page<\\/b><\\/h6>\\r\\n                                    <p class=\\\"text-justify\\\">\\r\\n                                        When user select any of the meal, it will route to meal detail page. Meal detail\\r\\n                                        can be fully customizable in admin dashboard by admin. In picture, wrote some\\r\\n                                        dummy text.\\r\\n                                        <br>\\r\\n                                        In detail page, it includes images of meal using slider and content of the meal,\\r\\n                                        price, order button and comment section for current meal with rating(used select\\r\\n                                        option because of course limitation).\\r\\n                                        <br>\\r\\n                                        User can order the food with desire amount and it will add to the cart if user\\r\\n                                        clicks on add to cart button and if user clicks on order button it will route to\\r\\n                                        order page to confirm order and make purchase.\\r\\n                                    <\\/p>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593403342\\/minlwinkyaw\\/restaurant\\/6_ozxwgh.png\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-lightbox=\\\"online_food_order\\\"\\r\\n                                       data-title=\\\"Cart List\\\">\\r\\n                                        <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/minlwinkyaw\\/image\\/upload\\/v1593403342\\/minlwinkyaw\\/restaurant\\/6_ozxwgh.png\\\"\\r\\n                                             class=\\\"img-responsive img-fluid\\\"\\r\\n                                             alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                                    <\\/a>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\n                                <div class=\\\"col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 py-3\\\">\\r\\n                                    <h6><b>Cart List<\\/b><\\/h6>\\r\\n                                    <p class=\\\"text-justify\\\">\\r\\n                                        In the cart list page, it will show list of the foods user added to the cart and\\r\\n                                        user can order individual item from the cart or all of them at the same time.\\r\\n                                        There is delete option to remove items from the cart as well.\\r\\n                                    <\\/p>\\r\\n                                <\\/div>\\r\\